definitions.definition: A small Arctic and Subarctic rodent from any of six genera of similar rodents.
Any member of a group given to conformity or groupthink , especially a group poised to follow a leader off a cliff .

main_definition: A small Arctic and Subarctic rodent from any of six genera of similar rodents.
secondary_definitions: ( figuratively ) Any member of a group given to conformity or groupthink , especially a group poised to follow a leader off a cliff .
